@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

@prefix ex: <http://example.org/data/> .

<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Environment> a owl:Class, rdfs:SubClassOf [ a owl:Class ] .
<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Component> a owl:Class, rdfs:SubClassOf [ a owl:Class ] .
<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Location> a owl:Class, rdfs:SubClassOf [ a owl:Class ] .
<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> a xsd:Datatype.

<ex:CurrentEnvironment> a psr:Environment .
<ex:ObjectOnTable> a psr:Component, rdfs:isDefinedBy <ex:CurrentEnvironment> .
<ex:Table> a psr:Component, rdfs:isDefinedBy <ex:CurrentEnvironment> .

<ex:OpeningOnObject> a psr:Affordance, rdfs:isDefinedBy [ a <ex:CurrentEnvironment> ] .

<ex:Door> a psr:Component, rdfs:isDefinedBy [ a <ex:CurrentEnvironment> ] .

<ex:ClosingOnDoor> a psr:Affordance, rdfs:isDefinedBy [ a <ex:CurrentEnvironment> ] .

<ex:PushingOnObject> a psr:Affordance, rdfs:isDefinedBy [ a <ex:CurrentEnvironment> ] .

<ex:GraspingOnObject> a psr:Affordance, rdfs:isDefinedBy [ a <ex:CurrentEnvironment> ] .
